system1.name: Tabor
system1.info: This system contained Tabor V; a planet controlled by the Snake's Guild.

system2.name: Vagadarr
system2.info: The Vagadarr system was a star system that contained an unidentified planet.

system3.name: Mykapo
system3.info: The Mykapo system was a star system located in the galaxy that contained the planet Mykapo and its lone sun. A group of Krawg pirates operated in the Mykapo system.

system4.name: Tertiary Usaita
system4.info: The Tertiary Usaita system was a barren star system, compromised mostly of dust and rock that orbited the red dwarf Tertiary Usaita. It was marked by a navigational beacon that had been left by a survey team from the Old Republic thousands of years before the Galactic Civil War.

system5.name: Hartaga
system5.info: The Hartaga system was a star system that contained Kiara's Comet Cluster.

system6.name: Jalindi
system6.info: The Jalindi system was a star system located in the galaxy that contained the planet Jalindi.

system7.name: Kellux
system7.info: The Kellux system was a star system that contained the planet Kellux.

system8.name: Kudo
system8.info: The Kudo system was a star system located in the galaxy that contained Kudo, as well as its third moon, Kudo III. During the Galactic Civil War, the Star Destroyer Celerity was disabled in the Kudo system, and the 204th Imperial Fighter Wing were tasked with protecting a maintenance crew aboard the Summit. Upon entering the system, the cruiser was attacked by TIE fighters.
